org.apache.juddi.api.impl

Class UDDIv2PublishImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.juddi.api.impl.UDDIv2PublishImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.uddi.v2_service.Publish

    public class UDDIv2PublishImpl
extends Object
implements org.uddi.v2_service.Publish
    UDDI v2 Implementation for the Publish service. This implementation is basically a wrapper and API translator that translates and forwards the request to our UDDIv3 Publish implementation

    This class is a BETA feature and is largely untested. Please report any issues
    Since:
    3.2
    Author:
    Alex O'Ree
